      "message": "nit: Handling of this stuff is very hard to follow :-/ Maybe \"if r.State {\" can be refactored into be a separate loop:\n\nq.Run(...) loop (perhaps collecting *coordinator.LogStream)\nif r.State {\n  another loop that deals with LogStreamState specifically\n}",
